					Full Description



		PT Dyandra Media International Tbk is an Indonesia-based holding company primarily engaged in meetings, incentives, conventions and exhibitions (MICE) industry. It offers integrated event solutions. Through its subsidiaries, it operates four business lines: event organizing, event supporting business, convention and exhibition hall and hotel. PT Dyandra Promosindo, operating the event organizing business, organizes various regular major exhibitions in Indonesia, such as Indonesia Celullar Show and Indocomtech. PT Dyamall Graha Utama, managing its event supporting business, provides event supporting services, such as concept designing and event equipment provisioning. PT Nusa Dua Indonesia, managing its convention and exhibition hall business, operates various venues, such as Bali Nusa Dua Convention Center and Gramedia Expo. PT Graha Multi Utama, managing the hotel business, operates a chain of hotels under Amaris, Santika, Santika Premier and Santika Premier Dyandra brand names.
» Full Overview of DYAN.JK







