Company Description                    




                        PT. Dyandra Media Internasional Tbk. (DYAN) is a provider of event solutions in Indonesia. DYAN is the holding company that manages the various lines of business of Dyandra Group. Through subsidiaries, DYAN operates in four business lines namely: Event/Exhibition Organizer, Convention & Exhibition Hall, Hotels, and Event Support Business. DYAN was listed on Indonesia Stock Exchange in 2013 under the Main Board. The company was founded in 2007 and based in Jakarta, Indonesia.                    


